Add this respective scripts to cron to run all the time in background.
# m h  dom mon dow   command
* * * * * DISPLAY=:0 <dir>/low_memory_alert.sh 
* * * * * DISPLAY=:0 <dir>/cpu_gpu_temp_alert.sh


Create a dir ~/.byobu/bin and add the file with a priority number. Lower number means higher prioity.
